{"data":{"allAboutMarkdown":{"sections":[{"frontmatter":{"imageAlt":"About me as a developer...","imageSrc":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/c6cd448ea4a87d8e98ad7ae0d969d58a/8c33b/profile-pic2.png","srcSet":"/static/c6cd448ea4a87d8e98ad7ae0d969d58a/36de9/profile-pic2.png 100w,\n/static/c6cd448ea4a87d8e98ad7ae0d969d58a/54af2/profile-pic2.png 200w,\n/static/c6cd448ea4a87d8e98ad7ae0d969d58a/8c33b/profile-pic2.png 400w","sizes":"(min-width: 400px) 400px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/c6cd448ea4a87d8e98ad7ae0d969d58a/f35a7/profile-pic2.webp 100w,\n/static/c6cd448ea4a87d8e98ad7ae0d969d58a/cafa8/profile-pic2.webp 200w,\n/static/c6cd448ea4a87d8e98ad7ae0d969d58a/50ed4/profile-pic2.webp 400w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 400px) 400px, 100vw"}]},"width":400,"height":463}}}},"html":"<p>As a developer I gained experience working with technologies ranging from Visual Basic and C# for desktop software, to PHP, JavaScript, HTML, and CSS for web applications.</p>\n<p>I honed these skills by working with frameworks like CodeIgniter, Laravel, and jQuery, developing large-scale projects in finance, inventory, sales, and accounting.</p>\n<p>I also had the opportunity to work with ERP systems such as Microsoft Dynamics SL and develop custom modules in Visual Basic.</p>\n<p>I am a self-taught developer who keeps learning constantly, always looking to improve my skills and deliver better solutions to reach team goals.</p>"}]}}}